<div class="container">
  <h1>Coerced to create a blog out of thin air.</h1>
  <p>Cheryll's Magic Show to be presented to Master Teng (just before crying)!</p>
  <a href="http://tinypic.com?ref=2mmeghs" target="_blank"><img src="http://i62.tinypic.com/2mmeghs.png" border="0" alt="Image and video hosting by TinyPic"></a>
  <p><a href="/posts/create">Create a new post!</a></p>
